              "name": "The dangers of comparing God to the \"universe\" ",
              "datePublished": 1624568400,
              "description": "<p>Hey Squeeze fam! We're kicking the summer off with season 2. This Thursday me and Sean Fowler discuss the spiritual practices of new age. This is a practice that is very prevalent today. New age is a range of religious or spiritual beliefs that include beliefs in reincarnations, astrology, psychics, and the presence of spiritual energy in physical objects. How does this interfere with God? Can you be a believer and practice new age? Tune in to S2 EP 1 to hear not only what me and Sean discuss, but also what scripture says.&nbsp;</p>\n",
              "audioUrl": "https://anchor.fm/s/268b4bbc/podcast/play/36117554/https%3A%2F%2Fd3ctxlq1ktw2nl.cloudfront.net%2Fstaging%2F2021-5-24%2F04e83461-7064-73b2-ff1b-3e8219d087bc.mp3",
