              "uuid": "907940b0-87fb-4928-8b5a-eecd5c86b9af",
              "name": "MAINTAINING OUR NEW YEAR GOALS | EP 16",
              "datePublished": 1611529200,
              "description": "New Year goals are often jotted down...and then forgotten about. We spend hours thinking about how the next year will be different, but we often times fail at achieving those goals. In this episode I speak on practical ways we can maintain our New Year goals. \n",
              "audioUrl": "https://anchor.fm/s/268b4bbc/podcast/play/25664841/https%3A%2F%2Fd3ctxlq1ktw2nl.cloudfront.net%2Fstaging%2F2021-0-24%2Fa946aa0e-aba6-9e9e-b3e3-00a732146bd8.mp3",
