              "name": "LET'S SETTLE THIS | THE ROOMMATE SERIES EP 2",
              "datePublished": 1599777315,
              "description": "Welcome to episode 2 of The Roommate Series. In this episode we talk about a huge social topic within the black community amongst college students and that is the HBCU vs PWI debate. Are there misconceptions? Do HBCU students really think black PWI attendees deserve to experience racism at their institution? Listen to Let's Settle This and not only hear from me and my roommates who attend a PWI, but also HBCU grad; Michael N. Weaver Jr. \n",
              "audioUrl": "https://anchor.fm/s/268b4bbc/podcast/play/19397387/https%3A%2F%2Fd3ctxlq1ktw2nl.cloudfront.net%2Fstaging%2F2020-8-10%2Fb0547cad-c963-3f51-5d34-0b374a599b73.mp3",
