              "datePublished": 1599171385,
              "description": "Hey Squeeze fam. Welcome to The Roommate Series. Listen in on this three week series as me and my roommates speak on real, deep social topics in today's time. On this episode: SIS, YOU LOOK GOOD we discuss body positivity. We speak on body shaming, diet culture, plastic surgery, if we think there is a thin privilege, and much more! \n",
