              "name": "COLLEGE DURING QUARANTINE | EP 10",
              "datePublished": 1598567827,
              "description": "Happy Thursday and happy upload day Squeeze fam! It's syllabus week here at Mizzou and classes hare back in session for most. In this episode of COLLEGE DURING QUARANTINE me and my roommate speak on just that; our college experience during a pandemic. Are colleges really practicing social distancing? Is the quality of learning any different? Are people still going to the bars? Listen to episode 10 to find out. \n",
