              "description": "Happy Thursday and happy upload day! On episode 9, me and Israel dig into the layers of mental health. We discuss mental health in today's generation, previous generations, in the black and latin community, as well as with Christians. Also, are mental illnesses genetic? Listen to \"LET'S NORMALIZE THIS\" to find out. \n",
