              "name": "THE DEPTH OF COLORISM | EP 8",
              "datePublished": 1596750389,
              "description": "Happy Thursday and happy upload day! EP 8 goes in depth with colorism. We dive into how colorism affects the different shades of brown, including someone who isn't black but may still experience colorism. In this episode, Sean Fowler and Israel Hernandez joins me speaking on personal experiences with colorism in our own communities; black and Latin. Sean also discusses his Instagram live series \"Black Love United\" which covers the conversation, is black love possibly fading away. \n",
