              "description": "Hey Squeeze fam! Today me and Shadale Johnson continue \"WOULD YOU DATE ME?\" In this Part 2 episode we speak on our listeners thoughts on singleness and dating in 2020. How do you know if a guy or girl is playing you and what do people mean when they say I'm just  \"going with flow\"? \n",
