              "description": "Hey Squeeze fam! Thanks for tuning into EP 6. In this episode me and Shadale Johnson share our thoughts on singleness and dating in 2020. We also discuss how colorism can play a role in today's dating life. Be sure to leave a comment under today's Instagram post or DM The Squeeze on your thoughts or personal experiences with singleness or dating. Stay tuned for Part 2 next week. \n",
