              "description": "Hey Squeeze fam! On EP 4 of The Squeeze, Kevin Johnson and I speak on a \"trendy\" behavior in today's society, \"Cancel Culture\". Is it appropriate to cancel someone based off a dumb decision they've done years ago or do you think that's extreme? Me and Kevin discuss the different \"levels\" of cancel culture, from public figures to major companies. \n",
