              "description": "Hey Squeeze fam! Thanks for joining me on Episode 2 of The Squeeze. On this episode my friend Kyla joins me as we discuss how college has changed us, and what our outlook on college looked like during high school. If you would love to share any fun or crazy college stories of your own, please feel free to leave a comment under today's Instagram post and I would love to share them on next week's episode! \n",
